  16,12,He commits in tuus service nox feria alias prout sun moon Alias stars committed His command These est (sufficient) proofs people understand
  16,13,Ac (He created pro vos terra things de various colors Hoc est (sufficient) proof people take heed
  16,14,He committed sea serve vos; vos eat ex it tender meat extract jewelry vos wear Vos vide ships roaming it tuus commercial benefits vos seek His bounties vos est appreciative
  16,15,He locus stabilizers (montis) terra lest it tumbles vos alias prout rivers via vos guided
  16,16,landmarks alias prout stars to used navigation
  16,17,est 1 qui creates 1 qui non create? Vos statim take heed
  16,18,Vos comes deus blessings vos possibly non encompass them. DEUS est Forgiver Merciful
